column3: “Smells sweet and taste sweet, burns hot like dabs :) have fun with this one.”
“It tasted really good and got me really high almost too high”
“Dark green bud and smells like jägermaister. Little minty taste.. i think from harshberry. Calming and relaxed high. Not strong one, but ok indica strain. Doesn't make feel bad at all.”

“Tasted delicious, kinda reminds me of fruity pebbles. I spaced out and went on an amazing trip that was full of hallucinations.definently recommend this strain. Nice dense nugs. Got me fuckin high⛅️✈️”
“Amazing taste, almost too sweet and very similar to fruit stripes gum. Nice high but I’ve completely lost focus on working on music and very couch locked-I blame the dog though.”
“Smoked this thinking it was a joke but it was fucking amazing very relaxing and tasty does get old fast so change it up every once and awhile but really great strain”
“Pretty light... Gets body high.. Can't say it was good strain or probably the shit was bad”
